OL,3,CJustice for family of 'beloved' man as
OL,4,C'cold-blooded killer' jailed for life
OL,6,FThe family of a "kind and caring"
OL,7,FGloucester man have spoken of their
OL,8,Fgrief after seeing his killer jailed
OL,9,Ffor life.
OL,11,FKidane Gebrehiwot, 55, died after
OL,12,Fsuffering a single stab wound to his
OL,13,Ftorso during an attack outside his
OL,14,Fhome on Arthur Street, Gloucester, in
OL,15,FAugust 2023.
OL,17,FThe man responsible for his death,
OL,18,FSamwen Muiruri, was sentenced to life
OL,19,Fin prison on Thursday 29 August.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
