OL,3,CJustice for family of 'beloved' man as
OL,4,C'cold-blooded killer' jailed for life
OL,6,FA judge at Gloucester Crown Court
OL,7,Fdescribed him as a "dangerous man" who
OL,8,Fcan become "terrifyingly violent."
OL,10,FIn a victim impact statement, Kidane's
OL,11,Fdaughter Sosena said her father was a
OL,12,F"very good man."
OL,14,FShe said: "I have thoughts of his
OL,15,Fdeath in my dreams and can't focus on
OL,16,Fmy work. I am in pain. I lost my
OL,17,Ffather because he was killed by
OL,18,Fsomeone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
