OL,3,CJustice for family of 'beloved' man as
OL,4,C'cold-blooded killer' jailed for life
OL,6,F"I miss my father so much that I am
OL,7,Fstruggling to finish writing this. He
OL,8,Fwould call me before I go to sleep.
OL,9,FNow I will always be waiting for his
OL,10,Fphone call."
OL,12,FKidane's sister Hellen added: "From
OL,13,Fthe time when my brother was
OL,14,Fgruesomely attacked and murdered I
OL,15,Flost the full confidence of my life.
OL,17,F"Every morning when I wake up I have
OL,18,Fto remind myself that people like the
OL,19,Fman who stabbed my brother will be
OL,20,Fable to hurt me.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
