OL,3,CJustice for family of 'beloved' man as
OL,4,C'cold-blooded killer' jailed for life
OL,6,F"I used to love going out and getting
OL,7,Ftogether with family and friends until
OL,8,Fhe took Kidane's life away."
OL,10,FAt the conclusion of sentencing
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Adam Stacey from
OL,12,Fthe Major Crime Investigation Team
OL,13,Fsaid: "Kidane was a beloved member of
OL,14,Fthe community who was known for his
OL,15,Fkind and caring nature. He was known
OL,16,Fas 'Uncle'.
OL,18,F"Samwen Muiruri on the other hand is
OL,19,Fan extremely dangerous, violent
OL,20,Findividual and a coward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
