OL,3,CJustice for family of 'beloved' man as
OL,4,C'cold-blooded killer' jailed for life
OL,6,F"Having been put in his place by
OL,7,FKidane during an argument on Eastgate
OL,8,FStreet he headed home, picked up a
OL,9,Fknife and returned to attack Kidane in
OL,10,Fwhat was a cold-blooded and pre-
OL,11,Fmeditated act of extreme violence."
OL,13,F"He has a propensity for such violence
OL,14,Fand our communities are safer with him
OL,15,Fbehind bars," he added.
OL,17,FHanding down his sentence, His Honour
OL,18,FJudge Blair KC described Muiruri as "a
OL,19,Fcoward" for not pleading guilty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
