OL,3,CJustice for family of 'beloved' man as
OL,4,C'cold-blooded killer' jailed for life
OL,6,FHe also described him as "a man who
OL,7,Fcan become terrifyingly violent if
OL,8,Fcrossed by others."
OL,10,FHe told the court that it is clear
OL,11,FKidane Grebrehiwot is going to be
OL,12,F"deeply missed" by those who knew him.
OL,14,F"From what has emerged during the
OL,15,Fcourse of this trial, I have heard how
OL,16,FKidane Gebrehiwot was a kind hearted
OL,17,Fman.
OL,19,F"In Amarinya, 'Gebrehiwot' means
OL,20,F'Servant of Life'. I am sure that is
OL,21,Fwhat he was to his family," he added.
